<section class="industries" id="industries">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="shead reveal">
      <span class="kicker">Built For Your Industry</span>
      <h2>Training That Fits The Way <em>You</em> Actually Work</h2>
      <p>Generic First Aid Isn't Enough When You're Being Audited, Insured Or Inspected. We Tailor Every Course To Your Environment, Your Risks And Your Compliance Obligations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ind-grid">

      <div class="ind reveal">
        <div class="top">
          <div class="ic">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 21h18M5 21V8l7-4 7 4v13M9 21v-6h6v6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>High-Risk Worksites</h3>
            <div class="who">Construction · Mining · Manufacturing</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>Strict WHS Obligations And Heavy Penalties For Non-Compliance. We Deliver The Exact Units Of Competency You Need, On Your Schedule, With The Documentation Auditors Demand.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> HLTAID009 / 011 Mapped To Your Refresher Cycle</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Scenarios Built Around Site Hazards — Trauma, Crush, Chemical</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Flexible Scheduling To Minimise Downtime</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ind reveal">
        <div class="top">
          <div class="ic">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M3 9l9-5 9 5-9 5-9-5zM7 11v5c0 1 2 3 5 3s5-2 5-3v-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Education &amp; Childcare</h3>
            <div class="who">Schools · Daycare · OOSH</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>The Stakes Are Highest Where The Clients Are Children. We Deliver The Education &amp; Care Unit With Trainers Skilled In Paediatric Emergencies — And We Work Around Your Term And Holiday Windows.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> HLTAID012 — First Aid In An Education &amp; Care Setting</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Asthma, Anaphylaxis &amp; Choking Focus For Kids</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Booked Into School-Holiday &amp; Pupil-Free Days</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ind reveal">
        <div class="top">
          <div class="ic">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M4 8h16l-1 12H5L4 8zM8 8V6a4 4 0 018 0v2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Hospitality &amp; Events</h3>
            <div class="who">Restaurants · Hotels · Venues</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>High Turnover Means Constant Re-Training. We Keep New Hires Compliant Fast, With Blended Options That Fit Around Shift Work — So Staff Are Certified Before They Start.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Blended Online Theory + Short Practical Sessions</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Rapid Certification Turnaround For New Starters</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Burns, Choking &amp; Venue-Specific Scenarios</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="ind reveal">
        <div class="top">
          <div class="ic">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 21s-7-4.5-7-10a7 7 0 0114 0c0 5.5-7 10-7 10z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="11" r="2.5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Community &amp; Events</h3>
            <div class="who">Clubs · Groups · Coordinators</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>Tight Budgets, Real Liability. With No Dedicated Safety Officer, You Need Plain-English Guidance — We Tell You Exactly How Many Trained People, What Kit, And What Your Event Needs.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Jargon-Free Advice On Numbers &amp; Requirements</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> First Aid Kit Supply, Checks &amp; Restocking</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg> Group Rates &amp; In-Home Workshop Options</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
